  "elapsed_s": 17.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was so fed up with the-- when he heard this plot, because this was, was done all behind him, because the Americans had the SOS, special operation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But within that secret organization of the-- of the Americans, like the British had that the Jews served in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the CIA was operating there, even without or the consent of the president of the United States of America.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when Eisenhower got wind of it, what, what's this plot?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hear that they want to, that they want to send in, in George Patton with his army what is commanding in Italy, into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was stunned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody ordered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody authorized it, and so-- and Eisenhower demoted George Patton from general to colonel, to-- from an army commander to a, to, to a division, division commander.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this whole plot fell, fell, fell flat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, since it's straightforward question, stay straightforward answer, answer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The man was Gyorgy Egri.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Originally, I find out later, when I was, I was back, back in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But first, to tell you how, how I met with the man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I recognized that this man is in Toronto, and I recognize him as a planted agent, an informer, in [INAUDIBLE] prison when I was, I was kept prisoner in a Hungarian counterintelligence.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Gestapo had this headquarter in the same same military, military building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were all kinds of activities in those years, in the late '50s, and then in the '60s, the peace movement, especially the peace movement, worldwide, worldwide movement.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Toronto here, we had peace demonstrations almost every week, and meetings and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
